<i>adverb</i>: 푸근히 [푸근히], 포근히 [포근히], 조촐히 [조촐히], 고즈넉이 [고즈너기] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>푸근히 [푸근히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. cozily; snugly; softly</dd><br>
<dd>꽤 두꺼운 물건이나 자리가 부드럽고 따뜻하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of a quite thick object or seat being soft and warm.</dd><br>
<dd>2. comfortably</dd><br>
<dd>느낌이나 분위기가 부드럽고 따뜻하여 편안하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a feeling or atmosphere being comfortable because it is soft and warm.</dd><br>
<dd>3. warmly</dd><br>
<dd>날씨가 바람이 없고 꽤 따뜻하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In windless and quite warm weather.</dd><br>
<dt>포근히 [포근히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. cozily; snugly; softly</dd><br>
<dd>두꺼운 물건이나 자리가 보드랍고 따뜻하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of a thick object or seat being soft and warm.</dd><br>
<dd>2. comfortably</dd><br>
<dd>느낌이나 분위기가 보드랍고 따뜻하여 편안하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a feeling or atmosphere being comfortable because it is soft and warm.</dd><br>
<dd>3. warmly</dd><br>
<dd>날씨가 바람이 없고 따뜻하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In windless and quite warm weather.</dd><br>
<dt>조촐히 [조촐히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. cozily</dd><br>
<dd>작지만 아담하고 깨끗이.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of being small but petite and clean.</dd><br>
<dd>2. demurely</dd><br>
<dd>행동이나 행실 등이 깔끔하고 얌전히.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of being refined and dignified in behavior or deed.</dd><br>
<dd>3. neatly; simply</dd><br>
<dd>외모나 모습 등이 깨끗하고 멋이 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of being neat and classy in appearance or looks.</dd><br>
<dd>4. quietly; simply</dd><br>
<dd>조용하고 간단하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of being quiet and simple.</dd><br>
<dt>고즈넉이 [고즈너기]</dt><br>
<dd>1. snugly; cozily</dd><br>
<dd>조용하고 편안하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Quietly and comfortably.</dd><br>
<dd>2. quiety; gently</dd><br>
<dd>조용하고 소리가 낮게.</dd><br>
<dd>Quietly and with a low sound.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>